BookMyTime - Business Plan Document
Executive Summary
Company: BookMyTime Inc.
Tagline: "Your Time, Perfectly Booked"
Founded: 2024
Location: Remote-first, Delaware C-Corp
CEO: [Your Name] - Linguistic Tutor & Software Developer

Vision: To become the global standard for service-based appointment scheduling, empowering independent professionals and simplifying client bookings worldwide.

Mission: To build a secure, scalable, and accessible platform that enables service providers to efficiently manage their schedules while providing clients with a seamless, intuitive booking experience.

Product: A comprehensive scheduling SaaS platform connecting tutors, coaches, consultants, and other service-based professionals with clients globally. Built with TypeScript, deployed on AWS, featuring full accessibility, internationalization, and enterprise-grade security.

Current Status: MVP Development Phase (Week 1 of 20-week roadmap)

